{"tid":1296180,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求開個愛國台！","createTime":"2019-07-08T09:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T11:54:28.000Z","uid":79589,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dca4a5ced6ba90d97b27191a219b91c8b394ca12","tid":1296180,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:40:54.000Z","msg":"眾所鳩知，Sor，周知<br />\n連登巴絲都係愛國愛黨青年<br />\n08奧運時期係舊登時代，大家嘅愛國之心都表露無遺，網上求其search 都有一大堆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sngnTTv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsngnTTv.png&h=e12e6a50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每逢國家有乜天災，大家都落力捐錢，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有人禍更加會勇敢發聲，持續追蹤</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢種愛國之心，完全係發自內心，同一班為錢而撐嘅3毛5毛完全無得比！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係！近日逃犯條例，連登巴絲遭到前所未有黃屍入侵，比人打成係反港反國基地，加埋啲低質3毛言論係到煽風點火，完全污衊左一眾巴絲愛國情操！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以，我強烈建議要開個愛國台，表明連登愛國之心！</span></span><br />\n比一個集中分台討論<br />\n1. 國家時事<br />\n2. 國家政事<br />\n3. 同胞愛國言論分享，尤其係偉大嘅口交部發言人耿爽同志<br />\n4. 驅逐低質3毛5毛，令真愛國巴絲上水<br />\n5. 比一眾翻牆同志接觸港內愛國同胞<br />\n<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登人人愛國<br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f48dcf7fbfa52a00ec4af16a1f874f980409a95","tid":1296180,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"b765a066b2e636cbbedcd07765534a64f5ea3260","tid":1296180,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:42:55.000Z","msg":"我係中國人呀Hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd9554c87c4ed8903947c3cea1bb173ebbe4ebe","tid":1296180,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b765a066b2e636cbbedcd07765534a64f5ea3260","tid":1296180,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:42:55.000Z","msg":"我係中國人呀Hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咁比人屈我地反政府，冤枉呀"},{"pid":"ac31bd46f9a6e1221a77fd9ae80dcd03ad5a5567","tid":1296180,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:58:25.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"88b99da21a5f8b25687cd1cab82aad46a92acbee","tid":1296180,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727290815c7255972c3f26edac651f618c8e1609","tid":1296180,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0a35b00c5014aa423dad7f1b90ed910b0ca02141","tid":1296180,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:22:01.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d288a8bd3c4b8bed43403a16b0a1b9f0ebf29173","tid":1296180,"uid":274837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}